timelineItems.text: Luis Silva is down. Just what #RSL wants to see without Javier Morales on the pitch.

timelineItems.text: Salinas with great movement into the box, tries to turn around three people, sacred to shoot, then coughs it up right on schedule. #SJvRSL

timelineItems.text: Go Quakes #Quakes74 http://t.co/S3krz736My

timelineItems.name: John Marshall
timelineItems.text: It feels uncommonly muggy in San Jose today. #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: Danielle Ù

timelineItems.desc: The San Jose Earthquakes host Real Salt Lake in a vital Western Conference matchup.
timelineItems.title: HIGHLIGHTS: San Jose Earthquakes vs. Real Salt Lake | September 27, 2015

timelineItems.name: Garrett Cederquist
timelineItems.text: #SJ get a few chances in their attacking half. #RSL do well to repel. #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: San Jose Earthquakes
timelineItems.text: 21' HAVE A GO QUINCY! Takes down a ball from MPG with his chest, spins his body towards goal before rocketing a volley at Rimando! #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: Gary Singh
timelineItems.text: Now Salinas and Amarikwa working some magic in the box, but still no cigar. #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: Matthew Doyle
timelineItems.text: I really, really like Jordan Allen at RB. Hope they keep him in that spot permanently. #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: Garrett Cederquist
timelineItems.text: Just me, or does Plata seem to be moving slower? #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: San Jose Earthquakes
timelineItems.text: 25' GODOY!! MPG sends in a in-swinger, the ball bounces around to Anibal who hits a one-time ball just wide of the post. Still 0-0. #SJvRSL

timelineItems.name: Inside MLS
timelineItems.text: 25' 0-0: SAVE. Rimando manages to clear away corner with a thigh. RSL somehow navigates through the chaos. Danger averted. #SJvRSL #MLS

timelineItems.name: Garrett Cederquist

timelineItems.text: #SJvRSL #MLS #SoccerSunday It is gonna take 50 points just to MAKE the Western Conference playoffs this year.
